            <div type="question">
                <p>Share a memory of a holiday. Where was it, who went, what happened?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>The sun is shining and is  warming my heart. The blue sky is smiling   me  to bring  dream. The   light and cool wind is rocking me like a child. The birds  are singing to tell the aperitf  time with a  lot of friends. It is  a simple  moment  of peace and sharing. A soft wave of frienship  is dancing in my heart and my soul. I m happy</p>
            </div>
